{"type": "article", "id": 6133, "title": "Nike Flyknit Lunar 3 情人节配色款", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-12T07:24:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061352163ZlBs1oxOfEkdSNm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t耐克旗下明星系列 Flyknit Lunar 今年迎来第三代鞋款，在情人节来临之际，耐克特别推出两款男女情侣鞋配色设计，男款鞋头以黄绿配色交错编织而成，女款则注入了更多的粉红色调，同时 Swoosh logo 部分则融入了 3M 设计；而白色的中底部分则加入了泼墨细节点缀。当然 Flyknit Lunar 3 还是结合了 Flyknit 鞋面和 Lunarlon 鞋底两项品牌的专利技术，继续为用户家带来舒适的穿着体验。这两款特别配色将于今日正式登陆各大门店，售价 150 美元（约合人民币 937 元）。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135213vmcjxsPLMI58Q9dh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135214Rb1wPYHql23Vrdpj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135214uZDow3sy9gqinbjV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135215fZI0Vt1GDlb3jOrw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135215PHExVK0uar2UcnqN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135215pJHR5TKw2SP3OMlD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}